###Purpose:
##Track data migration validation progress for 12,000+ provider records across dual-system reconciliation

**Technologies:** Power BI Service, Power Query, DAX, SFTP integration

**Key Features:**
- Executive dashboard with KPI cards (Compliance Rate: 96.5%, Total Providers: 12K)
- Technical dashboard with issue categorization (Persistent/Recurring/Post-Fix)
- Trend analysis showing improvement from 95% → 96.5% over 6 weeks
- Color-coded status indicators and drill-down capabilities
- Automated refresh from daily SFTP extracts

**Business Impact:**
- Enabled executive decision-making on production cutover readiness
- Identified 152 specialty validation issues requiring remediation
- Provided real-time visibility to vendor and internal stakeholders
- Tracked progress toward 95% accuracy threshold for regulatory compliance
